title: Chew to CM: It's just Ku Nan's proposal, don't overreact
text:
More 
Penang Chief Minister Lim Guan Eng had overreacted to suggestions for Penang to be turned into a federal territory, said MCA vice-president Chew Mei Fun. 
In a statement today, Chew said that the matter was never discussed by BN's top leadership and it remains merely a suggestion by Federal Territories Minister Tengku Adnan Tengku Mansor.
